  "description": "<p>🔥 <strong>BRAND / SALES REPRESENTATIVE</strong></p>\n<p>(<em>Fresh Grads Welcome | Learn &amp; Earn</em>)🔥🔥</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>No experience? No problem. <strong>We train from zero!</strong> 💡</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>↘️📚 <strong>What You’ll Learn:</strong></p>\n<p>– Communication &amp; people skills 🗣️</p>\n<p>– Sales &amp; marketing strategies 📈</p>\n<p>– Confidence building &amp; personal growth 💪🏻</p>\n<p>– Leadership &amp; career development 📊</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>↘️💰 <strong>What You’ll Earn:</strong></p>\n<p>– Uncapped income!!! 💵💵💵</p>\n<p>– Travel opportunity ✈️🚎</p>\n<p>– Recognition + promotions 📜📯</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>↘️📍 <strong>Full-time</strong> | Singapore-based </p>\n<p>👥 Fun, friendly, and growth-minded team</p>\n<p>📲 Apply NOW!!</p>\n<p>📧 Or email to: mycv2586@gmail.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🚀 <strong>Start learning. Start earning. Start now. </strong>💥</p>",
